DataElement.preferredName: Hopkins Verbal Learning Test Revised Retention Percentage Value
DataElement.preferredDefinition: Percentage value based on result of trial 4 of Hopkins Verbal Learning Test-Revised or HVLT-R divided by higher score of trials 2 and 3 then multiplied by 100.
